sequenceDiagram
  participant Op as Operator
  participant Cap as Capture controller
  participant Pre as Preprocess
  participant Inf as Inference engine
  participant Grd as Grading engine
  participant UI as On-device UI
  participant Str as Local store
  participant Syn as Sync agent
  participant API as Cloud API
  participant MLOps

  Op->>Cap: trigger
  Cap->>Pre: multi-angle frames
  Pre->>Inf: normals + albedo
  Inf->>Grd: anomaly map + defect list
  Grd->>UI: pass/fail + grade + heatmap
  Grd->>Str: write per-slab record
  Str->>Syn: queue (offline-first)
  Syn-->>API: upload when connected (TLS)
  API-->>MLOps: consented images → DVC
  MLOps-->>API: new signed model bundle
  API-->>Syn: OTA bundle delivery
